ift","code":["var body: some View {","    VStack {","        MyView()","        MyView()","    }","}"]}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Creates a state property that stores an initial wrapped value."}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"references":{"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/State/init()":{"conformance":{"constraints":[{"code":"Value","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" conforms to ","type":"text"},{"code":"ExpressibleByNilLiteral","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"conformancePrefix":[{"text":"Conforms when","type":"text"}],"availabilityPrefix":[{"text":"Available when","type":"text"}]},"type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"init","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"()","kind":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui\/state\/init()","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/State\/init()","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Creates a state property without an initial value.","type":"text"}],"title":"init()"},"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/VStack":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/VStack","type":"topic","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A view that arranges its subviews in a vertical line."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"VStack"}],"url":"\/documentation\/openswiftui\/vstack","title":"VStack","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"VStack"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://OpenSwiftUI/documentation/OpenSwiftUI/State/init(wrappedValue:)":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"init","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"wrappedValue","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Value","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}],"type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Creates a state property that stores an initial wrapped value.","type":"text"}],"identifie